"42:13:22" : {s: 42, a: 13, w: 22, r: "فرق", t: "تَتَفَرَّقُوا۟", l: "تَفَرَّقَ", lc: 8, tl: "tatafarraqū", lb: "ভিন্ন ভিন্ন হওয়া",e: "be divided", b: "তোমরা পৃথক হও", i: "kamu berpecah belah", f: 1, rm: "to separate/distinguish/divide/split/decide. farqun - the act of distinction or separating. fariq - who separates, discriminates. firqun - separate part, heap. firqatun - band of human beings. fariqun - part/portion, some party or band of human beings. furqan - criterion of right or wrong, draft, evidence or demonstration, a name of The Quran, aid, victory, argument, proof, dawn, distinction.", ag: "فعل مضارع صيغة ٥ وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Imperfect 5th form and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPF", qual: "(V)", deg: "2", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "JUS", lu: "تَفَرَّقَ،فِرَاقُ،فَرِيقٌۭ،نُفَرِّقُ"},
